      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it feels different than just a \"random dream\". like, the jingle is so specific, it’s the exact same frequency they used in that commercial last week. and the weird thing is, the \"Aetheria\" logo looks more vivid in the dream than it does on my phone screen. it’s almost like it’s being beamed in. don't you think it's possible they're doing some kind of subliminal stuff to influence people while they sleep? like, wouldn't that be a way to bypass everything we usually filter out?",
